Wrapper class: is a class that allows to store primitive data as object

prirmitive data --------> Corresponding wrapper class
int                       Integer
double                    Double
long                      Long
char                      Charcter
String                    String


int a = 7;
Integer a1 = new Integer(7);

Auto-boxing
(*)
Integer myInt = 8;
(*)
Integer[] myIntArr = new Integer[10];
myIntArr[0] = 8;

Auto-unboxing
(*)
int value1 = myInt;
(*)
int value2 = myIntArr[0];
(*)
int value3 = 4;
